metadata.name: Piece of Paradise 1
metadata.description:
Self Portrait
Dimensions: 4000 x 6000
Resolution: 240x 240
Camera: Canon EOS Rebel T6i
Lens: 70mm F2.8 DG Macro Art

Every part of this set was thought out to help create a tropical mood.
- Warm tones come from the natural sunlight peaking in through the nearby windows.
- Body Jewelry added a fun sparkle and helped bring out those warm tones.
- Huge leaf brings nature into the photo. Having the leaf be a big tropical leaf helps the viewer place the location of where this could be.

Everything comes together to help convey a tropical paradise even though I am standing in my living room.
